Many thanks to Kevin Scannell and Darrin Speegle for making their 
English - Irish - Afrikaans lexicon available for incorporation
into this pair.

Many thanks to Samuel Murray for making his English - Afrikaans
wordlists on computer terminology etc. available for incorporation
into this pair.

The Suid-Afrikaanse Akademie vir Wetenskap en Kuns (South African
Academy of Science and Arts) allowed us to use their bilingual 
English-Afrikaans paramedic wordlist to improve this translation pair.

Thanks to Anrie from af.wikipedia.org and Friedel from translate.org.za
for their long standing patience in answering all my requests.
